::Firearm/Rex::

"Maximize!" Firearm yells as he touches the ground, transforming into his 
robot mode. The shot from Imprisoner, which was aimed at his tank threads, 
hits the ground near his feet, a grenade going over his head and exploding 
against a tree.

He turns to Imprisoner, his arm cannon set on heavy fire, firing at the bouty 
hunter with it while pulling out a rifle and firing at Predator.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Rex flies in through the hole Firearm made in the canopy, firing his missile 
launcher at Imprisoner.
